    outline: ["Why does Calgary's climate stress buildings more than most cities?", "What do chinooks and freeze-thaw cycles do to a Calgary home?", "How bad is hail in Calgary, and what should you check after a storm?", "What does Calgary's building stock mean for your project?", "A season-by-season maintenance checklist for Calgary properties", "When should you bring in a local contractor?"],
