    outline: ["Why is Airdrie growing so fast — and what does it mean for property owners?", "How does Airdrie's climate affect buildings and outdoor projects?", "Which Airdrie neighbourhoods have which kinds of housing stock?", "What should you check before starting a project in Airdrie?", "New build or established home: how project needs differ in Airdrie", "Nearby areas"],
