    outline: ["Why Is Beaumont's Housing Stock Different From Its Neighbours?", "How Does the Edmonton-Region Climate Affect Homes in Beaumont?", "What Should You Check Before Starting a Project in a New Neighbourhood?", "Planning Around Beaumont's Growth and Construction Pace", "A Pre-Project Checklist for Beaumont Property Owners", "Nearby Areas and When to Look Beyond Beaumont"],
